## System narrative maintainer sync

When any system narrative file is created or modified:

1. **Read** `agent-os/skills/system-narrative-maintainer/SKILL.md`.
2. **Update** the relevant table or section (Domains, Patterns, Flows, Policies) — do not duplicate per-folder detail that belongs in `OVERVIEW.md`.
3. **Cross-link** to folder overviews and skills when introducing a new cross-cutting pattern or policy constant.

See **`docs/reference/architecture/documentation-system.md`**.
